CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 28, 2006

[Cite as 04/28/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2065.]

DISCIPLINARY CASES

2005-0750. Columbus Bar Assn. v. Ross.

This matter came on for further consideration upon the filing of a motion by respondent for extension of time to pay costs. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the motion is denied.
